label("$(1,1)$", (1,1), SW);
label("$(1,2)$", (1,2), NW);
label("$(2,1)$", (2,1), SE);
label("$(2,2)$", (2,2), NE);
[/asy]

The set of points for which Bob arrives before 1:30 is the set of points to the left of the line $x = 1.5.$

[asy]
unitsize(2 cm);

draw((1,0)--(2,0));
