The set of points that satisfy both conditions is the shaded triangle below:

[asy]
unitsize(2 cm);

draw((1,0)--(2,0));
draw((0,1)--(0,2));
draw((1.5,0)--(1.5,2));
fill((1.5,1)--(2,1)--(2,2)--(1.5,2)--cycle,gray(0.7));
